{"iti4:0.1":"Itivuttaka 4 ","iti4:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","iti4:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti4:0.4":"Kodhasutta ","iti4:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti4:2.1":"“Ekadhammam, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ","iti4:2.2":"aham vo patibhogo anagamitaya. ","iti4:2.3":"Katamam ekadhammam? ","iti4:2.4":"Kodham, bhikkhave, ekadhammam pajahatha; ","iti4:2.5":"aham vo patibhogo anagamitaya”ti. ","iti4:2.6":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti4:2.7":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti4:3.1":"“Yena kodhena kuddhase, ","iti4:3.2":"satta gacchanti duggatim; ","iti4:3.3":"Tam kodham sammadannaya, ","iti4:3.4":"pajahanti vipassino; ","iti4:3.5":"Pahaya na punayanti, ","iti4:3.6":"imam lokam kudacanan”ti. ","iti4:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti4:4.2":"Catuttham. "}